data.description:
***PRICE IMPROVEMENT FOR A QUICK SALE***Sold as-is***
This three-bedroom, two-and-a-half-bathroom home features an open floor plan, abundant natural light, and sits on one of the largest fenced lots in the neighborhood. Upstairs, enjoy the comfort of new carpeting and an extra bonus room, perfect for versatile use. The backyard serves as an oasis with a recently extended deck and pavement, creating a relaxing outdoor space. Additionally, the updated bathroom vanities and a new HVAC unit add to the appeal of this meticulously maintained and thoughtfully enhanced residence.
